			                		</h4>
			            		</div>
			            		<div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
			                		<div class="panel-body">
			                    		<p>Smart Track's Guard Tour Patrol System optimizes the use of checkpoints by giving customers the ability to program questions and prompts to each checkpoint. For example, when an officer scans a certain checkpoint, he may be asked to record a temperature, check a fire extinguisher or lock a door. Once his or her action has been recorded, only then is the checkpoint complete. This additional activity is designed to leverage officer presence as much as possible, in order to capture and create high quality security data and increase the effectiveness of every asset in the field.</p>
			                		</div>
			            		</div>
			        		</div>

