			                		</h4>
			            		</div>
			            		<div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
			                		<div class="panel-body">
			                    		<p>Visual Roster is comprehensive guard force management tool where managers and officers can easily define, modify, log, print and review shifts, tours, checkpoints, officer activities, incident reports and dispatches. Using Visual Roster's intuitive drag-and-drop functionality, Supervisors can easily manage the day-to-day activities of their guards, and quickly make changes in any aspect of a tour.</p>
			                		</div>
